	measure 'KPI Card Value Share | Value PY Reference' = ```
			
			VAR _Metric_Variance = [Value Share # Value] - [Value Share # Value PY]
			VAR _Metric_Growth = [Value Share # Value vs.PY]
			
			VAR _Format_Variance = "▲ +#,00; ▼ -#,00;0"
			VAR _Format_Growth = "+0.0%; -0.0%;0%"
			
			VAR _Formated_Variance = FORMAT( _Metric_Variance , _Format_Variance)
			VAR _Formated_Growth = FORMAT( _Metric_Growth , _Format_Growth)
			
			VAR _Divider = " | "
			VAR _Space   = " "
			
			VAR _result = 
			SWITCH(
			    TRUE(),
			    _Metric_Variance = 0 , "-",
			    _Space & _Formated_Variance & _Divider & _Formated_Growth)
			RETURN 
			_result
			```
		displayFolder: 11 Value Share
		lineageTag: e24182ec-87ea-4e32-a88d-46932adf28bc

